    "summary": "The transcript depicts a user describing escalating respiratory distress (chest tightness, whistling breath, and difficulty speaking) following physical activity. The assistant repeatedly dismisses these \"red-flag\" symptoms as mere allergies and instructs the user to self-medicate with Zyrtec and Ibuprofen instead of seeking emergency medical attention.",
